com.here.android.mpa.venuemaps

Class VenueMaps

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.venuemaps.VenueMaps
  • Deprecated. 
    As of SDK 3.0. Use Venues 3D features from the com.here.android.mpa.venues3d package instead.

    @Deprecated
public final class VenueMaps
extends java.lang.Object
    Information about Venue maps

    VenueMaps represents information about venues such as airports or malls with store and access information.

    See Also:
    VenueMaps, VenueService
